README:
The functions in pstv_jcgs.R can be used to reproduce the figures in the article ``Statistical inference on errorfully observed graphs'' by Carey E. Priebe, Daniel L. Sussman, Minh Tang, Joshua T. Vogelstein to appear in the  Journal of Computational and Graphical Statistics.


http://arxiv.org/abs/1211.3601
description: Code to reproduce figures in "Statistical inference for errorfully observed graphs"
